data.description: This 4/2 house was completely remodeled in 2019.   Features: Stainless steel appliances, granite countertops in kitchen, stackable washer and dryer,  interior paint,  wood look vinyl flooring, carpet in all 4 bedrooms,  added bathroom off master bedroom, hardware on kitchen cabinets,  faucets in kitchen and bathrooms, ceiling fans, lights,  vanities in both bathrooms, toilets,  guttering, and central heat and air.   The foundation was stabilized in the hall.  This house also has a storm cellar and storage shed/workshop and a carport.  The hot tub will not stay with the property. Lone Grove School District.
